{% extends 'layout.html.twig' %}

{% block body_class %}page-abuse{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<h1>Report Abuse</h1>

<p>If you have received spam or abusive content from our service, please report it.</p>

<h2>How to Report</h2>

<p>Send an email to <strong>abuse@{{ primary_domain }}</strong> with:</p>

<ol>
    <li>Full email headers of the abusive message</li>
    <li>Description of the abuse (spam, harassment, phishing, etc.)</li>
    <li>Any other relevant information</li>
</ol>

<h2>Response Time</h2>

<p>We review all abuse reports within 48 hours.</p>

<h2>What Happens Next</h2>

<p>If we confirm abuse, we will take appropriate action which may include:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Warning the user</li>
    <li>Suspending SMTP access</li>
    <li>Terminating the account</li>
</ul>

<h2>Privacy Note</h2>

<p>We do not disclose user information to third parties except when required by law. 
See our <a href="/transparency/">Transparency Reports</a> for details on any legal requests we have received.</p>
{% endblock %}
